The responsibilities of the IT Function of a bank shall, inter alia, include:
(1) assisting the Senior Management in identifying, measuring, monitoring,
mitigating and managing the level of IT outsourcing risk in the bank;

(i) access by service providers to data at the bank or its data centre shall be on
'need to know' basis, with appropriate controls to prevent security breaches or
data misuse;

It shall also ensure that specified
procedures are consistent with business needs and legal and regulatory
requirements;

